      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A sharper Chardonnay for simple roast or lemon chicken. It works because the acidity keeps the meat lively and the wine stays mineral rather than buttery.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Chardonnay</p>
    </div>
