      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A smart fried or spicy chicken bottle because the sweetness and acidity reset the palate fast. It is especially useful when sauces or seasoning add heat.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Riesling</p>
    </div>
